MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-2501. Cincinnati v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 92-1464-EL-AIR. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal fi-om the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective December 7, 1994.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
